<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_d707b443-7454-43fa-8a39-4572c64731ed" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>B2D6</sptc><title id="_91053e26-8911-4693-becb-5ab1ce46a53c">Temperature control devices</title><archive-num>2019: TAS B2.6(d), Application 1 and Exemption 1</archive-num><subclause id="_0f4c7b89-242a-4b2d-9ce3-4f4a4c3eb98b" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_094f959a-6117-4169-94ce-eebee6a53000">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A temperature control device used to deliver <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1334_0.4.0.xml#_92b3a3dc-59e4-425f-909b-d8eb03e6460a" id="_df0c31a3-d521-44de-bce6-4a047895d562" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">heated water</xref> in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1655_1.28.0.xml#_c59b9c99-8790-4a71-8a7e-4952cd7b212b" id="_a15a95af-08e8-40c1-bba7-b95b50c38da9" scope="local" type="subclause">B2D5(a)</xref> must be a—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li>thermostatic mixing valve; or</li><li>thermostatically controlled tap.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_31797d9e-740a-4581-bd30-20db9f4c3ff5" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_8d13035f-0b17-4084-b76b-ab181bfd2e47">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A temperature control device used to deliver <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1334_0.4.0.xml#_92b3a3dc-59e4-425f-909b-d8eb03e6460a" id="_99b0976e-6a7e-4bbf-b9e3-0105eaa23441" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">heated water</xref> in accordance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1655_1.28.0.xml#_c59b9c99-8790-4a71-8a7e-4952cd7b212b" id="_bceb7cfb-e1b1-4e85-9ec0-bdeff7d9c879" scope="local" type="subclause">B2D5(b)</xref> must be a—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li>thermostatic mixing valve; or</li><li>thermostatically controlled tap; or</li><li>tempering valve; or</li><li>temperature limited water heater limited to 50°C in accordance with AS 3498.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_b0636cd3-5bdf-4b95-9c1d-8ae0b7e9b482" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_d2360b2a-f836-46a4-8174-daad589bb5e4">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>The <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_172eb37a-6279-4b65-b6bb-40a4fc1e6796" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> maximum delivery temperature must be achieved in accordance with AS/NZS 3500.4.</p></subclause><callout id="_a42945f4-4ad8-4083-bd54-a399bc138882"><callout-type ncc-info-type="application"/><p>B2D6 only applies to new and replacement <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1334_0.4.0.xml#_92b3a3dc-59e4-425f-909b-d8eb03e6460a" id="_725a9cf7-fdc7-4f3c-8a91-ca754d6d5c20" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">heated water</xref> installations.</p></callout><callout id="_ee5099b4-f7b8-4098-8b9c-0bbdf8883df8"><callout-type ncc-info-type="exemption"/><p>B2D6 does not apply to the replacement of a single <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1334_0.4.0.xml#_92b3a3dc-59e4-425f-909b-d8eb03e6460a" id="_46c08d42-5130-49ff-8407-911f461344de" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">heated water</xref> storage unit within a range or bank of heaters.</p></callout></clause>